## Worker endpoints
- `?wantlist=<user>` — Discogs wantlist proxy (uses stored token)
- `?inventory=<seller>` — Discogs seller inventory (KV cached 6h)
- `?catalog=<storeId>` — Pre-fetched Shopify catalog from KV
- `?url=<target>` — Generic CORS proxy for store websites
- `?vinyldisc=<query>` — Special POST proxy for Vinyl Disc
- `?refresh_catalogs` — Admin: trigger manual catalog re-fetch
- Cron every 6h: auto-fetches Shopify catalogs for Music and Riots, Discos do Baú, Flur

## UI features (as of v0.9.0)
- Dark mode toggle
- City toggle (Porto / Lisbon)
- Store selector with logos and city pills
- Grid view (large/small) and list view toggle
- Format filter badges (Vinyl, CD, Cassette, etc.)
- Text search across wantlist
- "Show only found" toggle, "Hide out-of-stock" toggle
- Per-store result filter (click a store pill to filter)
- Export to CSV
- Progress bar + skip button while checking
- Stores done log (shows found count per store)
- **Grouped pressings** (v0.8.0): items with same artist+title are grouped under a single card with a stack visual effect and accordion to expand all pressings
- **Saved state** (v0.9.0): wantlist, check results, credentials, store selections, view preference, and city toggles persist in localStorage across sessions. Stale results (>1h) show an amber re-check banner. Migrated from sessionStorage to localStorage.

## Matching logic
- **Discogs seller stores**: exact release ID match against inventory
- **Shopify stores (cached)**: `shopifyMatch()` — title must appear in product title, artist in title or vendor
- **Common Ground GraphQL**: `cgMatch()` — same logic + can exact-match by Discogs ID
- **Web search**: `textMatch()` — normalised text search in page body
- Text normalisation: lowercase, diacritics stripped, non-alphanumeric → spaces

## Known limitations / things not done yet
- Tubitek and Carbono stores are `web-tbd` (not implemented — unclear scraping approach)
- Matching for MusicBrainz/CSV sources can produce false positives (no release ID available)
- No mobile-optimised store selector layout
